collectionMetadata.name: Vessel Calls (>75 GT), Monthly
collectionMetadata.description:
Dataset shows the monthly number of vessel calls (>75 GT) and shipping tonnage by purpose. Only vessels that are more than 75 Gross Tonnes are included.
(Latest month figures are preliminary estimates.)
sources: Maritime and Port Authority of Singapore
collectionMetadata.managedBy: Maritime and Port Authority of Singapore
